description:

Each print is designed and printed on premium A3 (29.7cm x 42cm) textured 250gsm cardstock.

name: 25 x Wedding Menu Fans
description:
Just in time for summer, these wedding menu fans are perfect for an outdoor wedding.  

Measuring 15cm x 15cm and featuring a hand stamped handle, these menus are designed and printed on 250gsm textured white cardstock.

Just contact us with your wedding menu text, bride and grooms name, date and location of your big day and we'll do the rest.

On digital approval by you, we will then begin to assemble your fans together.  Please allow 2-3 weeks for completion depending on quantity and our current workload.  If your order is urgent, please contact us to discuss your timeframe.  

This listing is for a set of 25 fans, each single price is $2.50

If you wish to use a different colour scheme, let us know and we'll design the menu to suit your theme or colours.

Set of 25 Save the Date Banners

A gorgeous unique Save the Date Invitation, set your tone to your wedding with this lovely pastel pink, white and gold glitter mini banner.



Each letter measures 3.7cm in height with the overall banner measuring approximately 60cm.



Invites are placed in a glassine bag measuring 14.5 x 9.5cm and are accompanied by textured ivory envelopes.

Each Glassine bag comes with a large Save The Date and glitter gold flag sticker and is sealed with a matching pastel pink sticker.

 

Custom made to order, all we need is the quantity required, the bride and grooms name, and the date and location of your big day.



Want a different design ?  Leave us a message!

 

Please contact me if you have any additional questions.

Each invitation  is accompanied by a C6 Kraft Envelope

1 x Simply Lace Wedding Invitation

1 x C6 Recycled Kraft Envelope

name: 3D Hearts Guestbook Alternative/Home Wall Art
description:
A gorgeous alternative to a wedding guest book, this piece of art is created using quality 250gsm, slightly textured, natural white cardstock, which is backed on to a printed atlas graphic, also using 250gsm cardstock,

The total measurement is 30cm x 30cm and contains 35 cut hearts measuring 3 cm x 3.8 cm.

 Need more or less hearts?  Convo us!

Perfect for your home or for your wedding with guests writing a little note and their initials or name on each heart, or half a heart per guest.

If you wish to have a different graphic backing, please don't hesitate to contact us with your enquiry!!

 
Please note this item is unframed.  The particular shadow box frame in the photo can be easily purchased from ikea and is from their 'Ribba' range for $39.99.

Your item will be carefully packaged in a cello bag and a rigid cardboard backing for protection.

If you require instruction's for your wedding guests, please leave a note "instuctions required" at the checkout and we'll be sure to include them in your parcel!
